{"tid":1498232,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳沛然出blog問HA『處理「被警方拘留病人」的責任問題 』","createTime":"2019-08-23T10:20:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-23T10:25:15.000Z","uid":182061,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"12c6bb081d32b7c43b4cae6029909f128f32df26","tid":1498232,"uid":182061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T10:20:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://doctordaddysoccer.blogspot.com/2019/08/letter-to-HAHO-QandS.html?fbclid=IwAR1rAh-bA7-OCowKT2qnsj9TON4LLalsRAYyLF4fB00IhjAgXRZDDNGYs1k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdoctordaddysoccer.blogspot.com%2F2019%2F08%2Fletter-to-HAHO-QandS.html%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1rAh-bA7-OCowKT2qnsj9TON4LLalsRAYyLF4fB00IhjAgXRZDDNGYs1k&d=3B0aCwotxrbiSqfA1QWlAouQyocENDzUuJTHoiHzCac%3D&h=525dbb07\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://doctordaddysoccer.blogspot.com/2019/08/letter-to-HAHO-QandS.html?fbclid=IwAR1rAh-bA7-OCowKT2qnsj9TON4LLalsRAYyLF4fB00IhjAgXRZDDNGYs1k</a><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>致醫院管理局質素及安全總監鍾健禮醫生： <br />\n<br />\n處理「被警方拘留病人」的責任問題 <br />\n<br />\n醫院管理局總辦事處質素及安全部於8月22日透過電郵，發出處理「被警方拘留病人」小錦囊，引起各界關注。本人接連收到不少同事和市民的查詢，簡列如下： <br />\n<br />\n一、 小錦囊問題3指：「警察有權限制被拘留人士的對外通訊。醫護人員若未得警察同意下致電家人，有可能要負上刑事責任。」 <br />\n自醫管局成立至今，是否有醫護人員在工作期間，因為未得警察同意，致電被拘留人士的家人而被控刑事罪，詳情為何？<br />\n請列出所提及刑事責任的法律條文。<br />\n二、如果在公立醫院內有人看見罪案發生，在什麼情況下決定舉報或不舉報？請提供法律依據。 <br />\n<br />\n本人祈局方能盡快回覆，以釋公眾疑慮。 <br />\n<br />\n祝 <br />\n時祺 <br />\n<br />\n陳沛然醫生敬上 <br />\n2019年8月23日</blockquote>"},{"pid":"a441da494d5cb65e5687fe12a45880b10e05a922","tid":1498232,"uid":38109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T10:20:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d6fef75a5452d34699697a90d2f3e1e7e638d41","tid":1498232,"uid":245441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T10:21:49.000Z","msg":"單刀直入 言簡意賅"},{"pid":"617a47724b1e64c0c061fd687f815e973e2db36b","tid":1498232,"uid":119283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T10:23:22.000Z","msg":"佢真係良心,醫生 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0556649c761ccc0ebf95a8455bbec7138c4b29d3","tid":1498232,"uid":13343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T10:24:01.000Z","msg":"好想做醫護跟住瘋狂投佢票"},{"pid":"491dbc5f3e915811c6d13cf2cf86c576230739b5","tid":1498232,"uid":266226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T10:24:27.000Z","msg":"陳醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f994293cdd1911a1dc999d3bbb8dbc921d4603ee","tid":1498232,"uid":48667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T10:25:15.000Z","msg":"真係好在有陳醫生呢啲幫醫護界發聲"}]}